<div class="column centered">
	<div>
		<%= image_tag 'logo.jpg' %>
	</div>
	<div id="introduction" class="space_above" style="text-align: left;">
		<h3>
			<p style="width: 100%">
				&ldquo;As many as 750,000 people could die as Somalia's drought worsens in the coming months, the UN has warned, declaring a famine in a new area.&rdquo; — BBC News
			</p>
			<p style="width: 100%">
				&ldquo;The crisis in the Horn of Africa is a profound human disaster in the making and a warning to the world. More than 11 million Africans, mainly pastoralists in the dry lands of Somalia, Ethiopia, Kenya, Uganda and neighbouring countries, are at risk of starvation after two failed rainy seasons. They need urgent help to stay alive.&rdquo; — The Guardian
			</p>
			<p style="width: 100%">
				&ldquo;UNICEF estimates that about 25 percent of people in Kenya's far north are now suffering from acute malnutrition, including more than 37 percent of those living in the Lake Turkana area. Throughout the Horn of Africa the aid group warns that "millions of children and women are at risk from death and disease unless a rapid and speedy response is put into action."&rdquo; — The New York Times
			</p>
		</h3>
	</div>
	<div id="donate_big">
		<%= link_to 'Donate',  "https://fundraise.unicef.org.uk/Donate/ToEvent/e0d4ef9d-985d-4ea8-9d25-9f480084f22d?project_id=8&return_url=#{root_url}" %>
	</div>
	<div>
		<%= image_tag 'about/map.png' %>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="column">
	<h2>Meet the team</h2>
	<% @personas.each do |persona| %>
		<div class="persona">
			<h3><%= persona[:name] %> ● <%= link_to "@#{persona[:twitter]}", "http://twitter.com/#{persona[:twitter]}", :target => :blank %></h3>
			<h4><%= persona[:role] %></h4>
			<%= image_tag "about/#{persona[:img]}.png" %>
			<p>
				<%= raw persona[:desc] %>
			</p>
		</div>
	<% end %>
</div>

<div class="centered" id="thanks">
	Also thanks for the inputs of: Mariana Moura Santos, Nikolai Lyden and Stefano Belloro.
</div>